text: Frederic Drăghici (born 1 June 1913, date of death unknown) was a Romanian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Romanian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Reșița
